H0.text: What name is given to any part of a circle that is bounded by two radii and an arc of the circumference. Segment

H1.text: What name is given to any part of a circle that is bounded by two radii and an arc of the circumference. Wedge

H2.text: What name is given to any part of a circle that is bounded by two radii and an arc of the circumference. Slice

H3.text: What name is given to any part of a circle that is bounded by two radii and an arc of the circumference. Sector

A4.text: Sector: a region bounded by two radii of equal length with a common centre and either of the two possible arcs, determined by this centre and the endpoints of the radii.
